fields.description:
EUCA-10503 removes credential download functionality, we should remove any references to the related commands:

* euca-get-credentials
* euca_conf --get-credentials

we should also remove references to eucalyptus services on port 8443 (but do not remove 8773), such as:

{quote}
 Verify connection from an end-user to the CLC on TCP ports 8443 and 8773
{quote}

from:
http://docs.hpcloud.com/eucalyptus/4.2.1/#install-guide/preparing_connectivity.html

comments.body:
[~kmeredith], if there are specific references to credential download then those would need to be removed, e.g.

{quote}
 eucarc is in your credentials zip file
{quote}
